		<title type="html"><![CDATA[[.04] Minor item - Remove Sandbox]]></title>

		
		<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/viewtopic.php?t=14325&amp;p=86027#p86027"><![CDATA[
Create a new sandbox and add a FileRootPath setting to a DVD-RW or CD-R drive (D: or E:, for me):<br>FileRootPath=D:\Sandbox\%Sandbox%<br><br>Remove Sandbox:<br>"Please delete the contents of xxx sandbox before invoking this command."<br><br>Delete Contents gives:<br>"The sandbox is empty. There is nothing to delete."<br><br>Edit Configuration must be used to either delete the FileRootPath setting, or to delete the sandbox from the configuration file.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1376">Guest10</a> — Sun Dec 23, 2012 12:54 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
